" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家好尊重合約精神。<br />\n到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，唔該大家真係思考下。<br />\n仲要今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量<br />\n<br />\n希望大家得閒做少少文宣係關於香港獨立，不過要soft啲係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90dd199fc8898fc27358a8070bd6b2cd92c4b8c","tid":1378032,"uid":115799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8372c50ebda47b9c6c64f680e89b12c5feb15e90","tid":1378032,"uid":139964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"唔只罷兩日阿 要長期罷落去 呢兩日只係開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0aeac2853a4507092b57e2d96390c249140e77c","tid":1378032,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:08:55.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 倡議民陣搞全港罷工「前夕」大遊行，一齊罷工吧！香港人！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1375198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1375198</a><br />\n<br />\n求下你地幫一幫推，<br />\n說好勇武之後和理非接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個運動要突破, 不要磨爛席<br />\n民陣提出全港大聯署,<br />\n參加者需出示自身行業，<br />\n要求民陣舉辦<br />\n遊行日子